{"tid":2297462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國家用自來水「點火就燃燒」","createTime":"2020-11-23T09:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T15:01:50.000Z","uid":134993,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7bccdf10b45521f9ee80edd793e09f97bceef591","tid":2297462,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:49:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=60076&amp;page=&amp;snA=6029911&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60076%26page%3D%26snA%3D6029911%26last%3D&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnRSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=30bfb686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=60076&amp;page=&amp;snA=6029911&amp;last=</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國遼寧省盤錦市四營村驚爆一起公眾安全事故，有村民表示家用水龍頭流出的自來水「可以點燃」，洗手的時候常常感覺洗不乾淨，同村100多戶家裡都出現相同狀況，而且「這個情況已經很久了」；更離譜的是，早在夏天時他們就曾向自來水公司反映，對方卻說管不了，放任這種危害公安的潛在風險多個月！"},{"pid":"bf259486bddde221ae85eec561030ebb10ce85c4","tid":2297462,"uid":52271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"一定係美國佬搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d019d055f0c234a88333d151fea734184fa24cc","tid":2297462,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf259486bddde221ae85eec561030ebb10ce85c4","tid":2297462,"uid":52271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"一定係美國佬搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"俄佬石油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f126a33e72683da516410600e55500666566bf91","tid":2297462,"uid":261937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"發達啦！新能源啊"},{"pid":"8e5cc98fad849189bf865c82405dd9a81299ee6f","tid":2297462,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:00:22.000Z","